      <h2>第一百六十章 伊河（三）</h2> 
      <p style="margin-bottom:10px;text-align:center"><span class="CHTXT">双击滚屏/单击停止&nbsp;|&nbsp; <input onclick="ScRadio('radio1')" id="radio1" style="position:relative;top:2px" type="radio" checked="checked" /> <font onclick="ScRadio('radio1')">全站滚屏</font>&nbsp;/&nbsp; <input onclick="ScRadio('radio2')" id="radio2" style="position:relative;top:2px" type="radio" /> <font onclick="ScRadio('radio2')">当前滚屏</font>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <input onclick="AutoNext()" id="AutoNext" style="position:relative;top:2px" type="checkbox" checked="checked" /> <font onclick="AutoNext('xxx')">滚底翻页</font>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<font onclick="speed('man')" id="man">滚慢</font>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<font onclick="speed('zhong')" id="zhong" class="cur">滚中</font>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<font onclick="speed('kuai')" id="kuai">滚快</font>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<font onclick="ReHere()" id="ReHere" class="cur">恢复默认</font></span></p> 
